299
00:14:49,340 --> 00:14:49,880
It's so cold.

300
00:14:49,880 --> 00:14:51,460
You're not even wearing a coat.

301
00:14:51,460 --> 00:14:52,480
Here. Put this on.

302
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:53,240
Look!

303
00:14:53,870 --> 00:14:54,670
When it falls on the clothes,

304
00:14:54,670 --> 00:14:56,370
it really looks like a snowflake.

305
00:14:56,370 --> 00:14:57,840
It's exactly the same
as that in the pictures.

306
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:59,640
These are snowflakes actually.

307
00:15:00,980 --> 00:15:02,410
Haven't you been to Beijing before?

308
00:15:02,410 --> 00:15:04,030
Why is it still so novel to you?

309
00:15:04,030 --> 00:15:06,030
You think I can always see snow
when I'm in Beijing?

310
00:15:06,030 --> 00:15:06,770
Thank you.

311
00:15:06,840 --> 00:15:07,770
You're welcome.

312
00:15:08,720 --> 00:15:11,700
[Guest Room]

313
00:15:11,770 --> 00:15:12,860
Okay. Fine.

314
00:15:11,840 --> 00:15:13,450
[Seasons Change Hostel]

315
00:15:21,650 --> 00:15:22,130
Well...

316
00:15:22,650 --> 00:15:24,380
Your snowballs are like bombs.

317
00:15:25,650 --> 00:15:26,860
Did I hurt you?

318
00:15:43,090 --> 00:15:46,670
[Seasons Change Hostel]

319
00:15:44,750 --> 00:15:46,320
Anyway, it doesn't hurt
even when you fall down, huh?

320
00:15:46,320 --> 00:15:47,240
I'll give you a suplex.

321
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:48,440
No! I admit defeat!

322
00:15:47,350 --> 00:15:49,870
[A home away from home, only better.]

323
00:15:49,970 --> 00:15:53,810
[Guest Room]

324
00:15:53,860 --> 00:15:58,430
[Seasons Change Hostel]

325
00:15:57,390 --> 00:15:58,250
I admit defeat!

326
00:15:58,390 --> 00:15:59,270
I admit defeat!

327
00:15:58,500 --> 00:16:03,130
[Guest Room]

328
00:15:59,890 --> 00:16:01,750
