329
00:16:04,690 --> 00:16:05,750
Don't sit down yet.

330
00:16:05,890 --> 00:16:07,620
Let me wipe the snow off for you.

331
00:16:08,720 --> 00:16:09,980
I think after the snow,

332
00:16:10,250 --> 00:16:12,150
