343
00:16:42,700 --> 00:16:43,220
I hugged him

344
00:16:43,220 --> 00:16:44,880
and kissed him several times.

345
00:16:49,510 --> 00:16:50,460
In this period of time,

346
00:16:50,460 --> 00:16:52,520
I've been trying to digest this news.

347
00:16:55,440 --> 00:16:56,670
When I came back that day,

348
00:16:56,670 --> 00:16:58,110
I threw the script away.

349
00:16:58,840 --> 00:17:00,640
But I regretted it immediately.

350
00:17:01,170 --> 00:17:02,570
I went back to look for it,

351
00:17:02,740 --> 00:17:04,540
but I couldn't find it anywhere.

352
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:06,849
Maybe God

353
00:17:06,880 --> 00:17:08,440
wanted to teach me a lesson.

354
00:17:10,180 --> 00:17:11,310
Wait a moment for me.

355
00:17:12,890 --> 00:17:16,510
[Seasons Change Hostel]

356
00:17:31,250 --> 00:17:37,280
[Seasons Change Hostel]

357
00:17:39,270 --> 00:17:39,920
Here.

358
00:17:51,010 --> 00:17:52,250
[The Late Love,
written by He Sheng & Xu Shengli]

359
00:17:58,100 --> 00:17:59,150
How come you...

360
00:18:00,330 --> 00:18:02,060
This is something so precious.

361
00:18:02,070 --> 00:18:03,440
Don't lose it again.

362
00:18:08,350 --> 00:18:10,680
[The Late Love,
written by He Sheng & Xu Shengli]

363
00:18:19,330 --> 00:18:20,350
Alright.

364
00:18:19,380 --> 00:18:24,210
[A home away from home, only better.]

365
00:18:21,090 --> 00:18:22,250
Life is like

366
00:18:22,250 --> 00:18:23,580
stepping into the snow.

367
00:18:24,310 --> 00:18:26,720
It's inevitable to step into it unevenly,

368
00:18:26,920 --> 00:18:28,520
which is completely normal.

369
00:18:30,810 --> 00:18:32,290
But just like you said,

370
00:18:33,050 --> 00:18:34,960
spring will definitely come.

371
00:18:36,570 --> 00:18:37,940
Even if it were not to come,

372
00:18:37,940 --> 00:18:39,400
winter would also be nice.

373
00:18:46,070 --> 00:18:47,930
Actually, in this period of time,

374
00:18:48,250 --> 00:18:49,790
I was ready to give up.

375
00:18:53,180 --> 00:18:55,500
It wasn't until you asked me for help

376
00:18:55,500 --> 00:18:56,750
that I suddenly felt

377
00:18:57,940 --> 00:19:01,000
there was still something
to look forward to in my life.

378
00:19:03,270 --> 00:19:03,830
That was perfect,

379
00:19:03,830 --> 00:19:05,030
so I just took this chance

380
00:19:05,030 --> 00:19:06,960
to hit the pause button for myself.

381
00:19:07,290 --> 00:19:09,020
I sent some money to my parents.

382
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:13,370
I paid the rent to extend my stay
until after the New Year.

383
00:19:14,110 --> 00:19:15,360
Actually, I feel

384
00:19:16,880 --> 00:19:17,980
quite grounded.

385
00:19:20,440 --> 00:19:21,680
I've also realized that

386
00:19:21,680 --> 00:19:24,780
when a person is down on his luck,

387
00:19:26,400 --> 00:19:28,250
this feeling of being needed

388
00:19:29,480 --> 00:19:31,480
can actually help him save himself.

389
00:19:39,310 --> 00:19:40,170
Zhuang Zhuang.

390
00:19:43,750 --> 00:19:45,610
Thank you for letting me help you.

391
00:19:46,160 --> 00:19:48,160
I know you did it on purpose.

392
00:19:49,110 --> 00:19:50,270
I really needed it.

393
00:19:52,140 --> 00:19:53,070
Alright.

394
00:19:58,640 --> 00:20:00,310
Although saying
that the result doesn't matter

395
00:20:00,310 --> 00:20:02,310
sounds like I'm comforting myself,

396
00:20:03,030 --> 00:20:05,040
I really think that in this world,

397
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:06,560
