398
00:20:08,030 --> 00:20:10,000
Even going through countless hardships

399
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:11,640
won't drive me back home.

400
00:20:13,550 --> 00:20:14,440
Right!

401
00:20:17,580 --> 00:20:21,630
