Director Huang and the others
would be here too?

407
00:20:39,480 --> 00:20:40,290
I originally arranged for

408
00:20:40,290 --> 00:20:41,900
Director Huang and the others to come.

409
00:20:41,900 --> 00:20:43,700
But something came up for them
at the last minute.

410
00:20:43,700 --> 00:20:45,430
They're really unable to come.

411
00:20:46,980 --> 00:20:48,400
Hey, come in.

412
00:20:52,270 --> 00:20:52,800
Sit down.

413
00:20:59,380 --> 00:21:00,110
Have a drink.

414
00:21:04,400 --> 00:21:05,140
Thank you.

415
00:21:07,750 --> 00:21:08,810
I'm quite grateful

416
00:21:08,880 --> 00:21:10,340
that you could come today.

417
00:21:10,700 --> 00:21:11,240
Really.

418
00:21:13,400 --> 00:21:15,530
Today, I'm so eager to talk to someone.

419
00:21:16,830 --> 00:21:17,630
You know what?

420
00:21:19,510 --> 00:21:21,370
A movie I invested in two years ago

421
00:21:22,440 --> 00:21:24,300
is confirmed to lose money today.

422
00:21:26,420 --> 00:21:27,420
Four million yuan

423
00:21:28,850 --> 00:21:29,440
