424
00:21:32,270 --> 00:21:33,200
Let me tell you.

425
00:21:36,250 --> 00:21:38,050
Before I invested in this movie,

426
00:21:38,200 --> 00:21:39,330
there was a director

427
00:21:40,200 --> 00:21:42,000
