432
00:21:51,550 --> 00:21:53,150
If a movie isn't convincing,

433
00:21:54,510 --> 00:21:56,040
how could it not lose money?

434
00:22:03,050 --> 00:22:05,110
This is the price of using a new actor.

435
00:22:06,460 --> 00:22:08,430
But every good actor

436
00:22:08,920 --> 00:22:10,760
