444
00:22:24,750 --> 00:22:26,250
This is the entertainment industry.

445
00:22:26,250 --> 00:22:27,740
What does overnight fame mean?

446
00:22:27,740 --> 00:22:29,270
There is no overnight fame.

447
00:22:29,460 --> 00:22:31,660
There is only an exchange of resources.

448
00:22:36,180 --> 00:22:37,710
Do you want to be an actress?

449
00:22:41,900 --> 00:22:42,480
Okay.

450
00:22:44,570 --> 00:22:45,900
Do you want it or not?

451
00:22:47,830 --> 00:22:50,030
As long as you are confident and want it,

452
00:22:50,250 --> 00:22:51,510
I'll use my resources

453
00:22:51,510 --> 00:22:52,440
