454
00:22:53,420 --> 00:22:54,770
I'm sure it'll succeed.

455
00:22:58,750 --> 00:23:01,350
But the key is whether you want it or not.

456
00:23:11,070 --> 00:23:11,930
How about this?

457
00:23:12,200 --> 00:23:13,730
If you want to be an actress,

458
00:23:14,200 --> 00:23:15,960
come to the Lihua Hotel tomorrow.

459
00:23:15,960 --> 00:23:16,610
I'll talk to you

460
00:23:16,610 --> 00:23:18,610
about the script for the next movie.

461
00:23:20,680 --> 00:23:21,000
I...

462
00:23:21,460 --> 00:23:22,300
I'm sorry.

463
00:23:22,500 --> 00:23:24,250
You wouldn't understand
the things that I told you.

464
00:23:24,250 --> 00:23:24,910
Let's sing.

465
00:23:26,440 --> 00:23:27,300
Let's have fun.

466
00:23:27,980 --> 00:23:28,440
Come on.

467
00:23:29,530 --> 00:23:30,730
Are you going to sing?

468
00:23:31,240 --> 00:23:32,900
