♪ Forget about yourself ♪

480
00:24:27,180 --> 00:24:30,460
♪ Love someone wholeheartedly this time ♪

481
00:24:30,850 --> 00:24:33,600
♪ Forget about yourself ♪

482
00:24:33,970 --> 00:24:36,810
♪ Stretch out your hand ♪

483
00:24:37,620 --> 00:24:40,420
♪ Don't have any concerns ♪

484
00:24:41,020 --> 00:24:43,000
♪ Open your heart ♪

485
00:24:43,770 --> 00:24:46,600
♪ Don't hesitate anymore ♪

486
00:25:11,250 --> 00:25:12,330
Ranran.

487
00:25:13,330 --> 00:25:15,730
Right now, the sun is shining on you,

488
00:25:16,070 --> 00:25:17,980
and you're glowing.

489
00:25:18,330 --> 00:25:19,680
How should I describe it?

490
00:25:19,680 --> 00:25:22,160
You're just like an angel.

491
00:25:23,030 --> 00:25:23,650
Director.

492
00:25:23,790 --> 00:25:25,090
I don't want her to miss this chance

493
00:25:25,090 --> 00:25:26,130
because of me.

494
00:25:26,610 --> 00:25:28,810
I'd like to apologize to you. I'm sorry.

495
00:25:33,050 --> 00:25:34,530
Among all the people I've ever met,

496
00:25:34,530 --> 00:25:35,880
apart from my mom,

497
00:25:36,660 --> 00:25:40,270
you're the woman
with the highest standards.

498
00:25:42,380 --> 00:25:43,290
When I first

499
00:25:43,290 --> 00:25:44,380
met you,

500
00:25:44,380 --> 00:25:46,580
I just thought you were very beautiful.

501
00:25:46,700 --> 00:25:47,750
I really hope...

502
00:25:47,750 --> 00:25:49,280
What I'm trying to say is...

503
00:25:49,720 --> 00:25:51,010
I like you.

504
00:26:13,550 --> 00:26:14,950
Who is it? Nobody is here.

505
00:26:19,740 --> 00:26:20,830
Who is it?

506
00:26:23,460 --> 00:26:24,240
Ranran?

507
00:26:25,140 --> 00:26:25,940
What's wrong?

508
00:26:27,460 --> 00:26:28,880
I want to talk to you.

509
00:26:32,220 --> 00:26:32,770
Let's talk inside.

510
00:26:32,770 --> 00:26:33,830
