515
00:26:42,590 --> 00:26:43,460
Us?

516
00:26:44,570 --> 00:26:45,430
Confirming it?

517
00:26:47,460 --> 00:26:48,110
What is it?

518
00:26:50,940 --> 00:26:52,810
If you don't want to talk,

519
00:26:53,350 --> 00:26:54,220
