in the depth of winter?

523
00:27:22,010 --> 00:27:24,220
From Wang's flower shed
at the alley entrance.

524
00:27:24,220 --> 00:27:25,160
As I was in a hurry,

525
00:27:25,160 --> 00:27:26,360
I will tell him later.

526
00:27:32,960 --> 00:27:33,620
Have a seat.

527
00:28:07,460 --> 00:28:08,260
