528
00:28:18,550 --> 00:28:19,280
Liangliang.

529
00:28:22,980 --> 00:28:24,180
Do you like me?

530
00:28:27,920 --> 00:28:28,590
Yes, I do.

531
00:28:32,810 --> 00:28:33,530
Well...

532
00:28:35,350 --> 00:28:36,550
Do you love me?

533
00:28:42,980 --> 00:28:43,510
Yes, I do.

534
00:29:36,640 --> 00:29:39,380
W-What are you waiting for?

535
00:30:37,030 --> 00:30:37,830
What's wrong?

536
00:30:39,180 --> 00:30:40,030
No, no, no.

537
00:30:40,900 --> 00:30:42,010
No, no, no.

538
00:30:47,240 --> 00:30:47,750
Ranran.

539
00:30:51,570 --> 00:30:52,270
I want it.

540
00:30:53,610 --> 00:30:54,680
I really want it.

541
00:30:56,830 --> 00:30:58,810
I-I really want to confirm it, too.

542
00:30:58,810 --> 00:31:00,670
But we can't confirm it like this.

543
00:31:02,980 --> 00:31:05,160
I haven't formally
confessed my love to you

544
00:31:05,160 --> 00:31:06,960
or gone on a proper date with you.

545
00:31:07,090 --> 00:31:08,050
There are still so many things

546
00:31:08,050 --> 00:31:09,180
