547
00:31:12,380 --> 00:31:13,190
I like you.

548
00:31:13,920 --> 00:31:14,680
I love you.

549
00:31:16,420 --> 00:31:17,070
I want to give you

550
00:31:17,070 --> 00:31:18,560
