become a famous actress.

557
00:31:36,570 --> 00:31:37,350
However,

558
00:31:42,290 --> 00:31:45,420
I don't want to hold you back
from your choices.

559
00:31:47,880 --> 00:31:49,140
We can't do this today.

560
00:31:54,850 --> 00:31:55,910
Everyone!

561
00:31:56,160 --> 00:31:57,530
People from the health station are here

562
00:31:57,530 --> 00:31:58,880
to do the winter disinfection for us.

563
00:31:58,880 --> 00:32:00,140
Guys, please cooperate.

564
00:32:00,140 --> 00:32:00,880
If there's anyone in the room,

565
00:32:00,880 --> 00:32:01,660
come out for a while.

566
00:32:01,660 --> 00:32:03,010
It'll be done in a moment.

567
00:32:03,010 --> 00:32:04,010
If there's no one in the room,

568
00:32:04,010 --> 00:32:05,460
I'll just come in.

569
00:32:05,900 --> 00:32:08,030
Come on. Everyone, please cooperate.

570
00:32:09,050 --> 00:32:10,580
Let's start with this room.

571
00:32:11,400 --> 00:32:12,730
How long will this take?

572
00:32:12,880 --> 00:32:14,280
It'll just take a moment.

573
00:32:14,480 --> 00:32:16,050
Yes. You can just go back in a moment.

574
00:32:16,050 --> 00:32:16,460
Okay.

575
00:32:16,460 --> 00:32:17,520
Come on. This room.

576
00:32:19,420 --> 00:32:21,010
You two can disinfect this room inside.

577
00:32:21,010 --> 00:32:23,340
I'll go see
if there's anyone in that room.

578
00:32:23,700 --> 00:32:25,300
Liangliang, are you afraid?

579
00:32:25,720 --> 00:32:26,640
Is anyone inside?

580
00:32:26,640 --> 00:32:27,050
I...

581
00:32:29,500 --> 00:32:30,400
I'm afraid if they find out about this,

582
00:32:30,400 --> 00:32:31,480
I won't be able to explain it,

583
00:32:31,480 --> 00:32:33,080
and it'll be bad for you, too.

584
00:32:33,920 --> 00:32:35,660
Everyone has gone to work at this hour.

585
00:32:35,660 --> 00:32:37,190
Come on. This room. Come on.

586
00:32:40,380 --> 00:32:42,980
There are still three rooms left
on this floor.

587
00:32:45,550 --> 00:32:46,280
Liangliang.

588
00:32:48,070 --> 00:32:48,980
Come on. This way.

589
00:32:48,980 --> 00:32:50,110
I'm not afraid.

590
00:32:50,830 --> 00:32:53,430
Come on.
There aren't many rooms left. Come on.

591
00:32:56,320 --> 00:32:57,520
Is anyone in Room 116?

592
00:32:58,740 --> 00:33:01,160
Ranran, Zhuang Zhuang, are you there?

593
00:33:01,590 --> 00:33:03,650
I'll open the door if no one's inside.

594
00:33:07,900 --> 00:33:08,900
Northeasterner.

595
00:33:10,110 --> 00:33:10,720
I'm here.

596
00:33:11,680 --> 00:33:12,750
Wait a moment.

597
00:33:13,110 --> 00:33:14,170
Someone's inside.

598
00:33:14,420 --> 00:33:14,950
Alright.

599
00:33:17,330 --> 00:33:18,180
It's a girl.

600
00:33:19,460 --> 00:33:20,890
Wait a moment.

601
00:33:23,880 --> 00:33:25,610
Ranran, hurry up.

602
00:33:26,610 --> 00:33:29,410
They still have to
go to several more places later.

603
00:33:29,880 --> 00:33:31,170
Guys, have some water.

604
00:33:31,770 --> 00:33:32,880
Ranran, hurry up.

605
00:33:35,350 --> 00:33:36,940
Ranran, hurry up.

606
00:33:40,140 --> 00:33:41,350
Ranran, hurry up.

607
00:33:41,420 --> 00:33:43,680
Yours is the only room left on this floor.

608
00:33:55,250 --> 00:33:56,180
The comrades from the health station

609
00:33:56,180 --> 00:33:57,830
are here to disinfect rooms for us.

610
00:33:57,830 --> 00:33:59,030
What the heck is that?

611
00:33:59,850 --> 00:34:00,610
Who is this?

612
00:34:01,880 --> 00:34:02,570
Ranran.

613
00:34:03,070 --> 00:34:03,960
Who are you?

614
00:34:09,030 --> 00:34:09,570
It's me.

615
00:34:09,960 --> 00:34:10,920
Tao Liangliang?

616
00:34:11,210 --> 00:34:12,469
Don't mention my name.

617
00:34:17,260 --> 00:34:18,050
I'm stuck.

618
00:34:20,190 --> 00:34:21,320
Go get some help now!

619
00:34:21,530 --> 00:34:22,300
It hurts!

620
00:34:29,780 --> 00:34:30,440
How are you?

621
00:34:31,880 --> 00:34:32,989
Look at this. Look.

622
00:34:33,480 --> 00:34:34,580
It's bleeding.

623
00:34:34,840 --> 00:34:35,960
I'll help you apply the medicine.

624
00:34:35,960 --> 00:34:37,560
No, no, no. I'll do it myself.

625
00:34:37,690 --> 00:34:39,260
I'm afraid you'll do it in a rough way.

626
00:34:39,260 --> 00:34:39,650
What?

627
00:34:40,260 --> 00:34:41,690
You asked for this yourself, didn't you?

628
00:34:41,690 --> 00:34:42,980
There has been one drama after another.

629
00:34:42,980 --> 00:34:44,380
It's all a show this time.

630
00:34:44,440 --> 00:34:45,840
This is nothing serious.

631
00:34:49,460 --> 00:34:50,440
What a lunatic.

632
00:34:50,530 --> 00:34:51,790
I hope it really hurts.

633
00:34:52,900 --> 00:34:54,170
It hurts so much.

634
00:34:56,940 --> 00:34:58,400
But guys, please...

635
00:34:59,630 --> 00:35:02,530
keep it a secret for me.

636
00:35:02,820 --> 00:35:04,480
How should we keep it a secret?

637
00:35:04,550 --> 00:35:06,030
All the people saw it.

638
00:35:07,340 --> 00:35:07,820
Bro,

639
00:35:08,280 --> 00:35:09,840
that's one of the four great joys in life.

640
00:35:09,840 --> 00:35:10,860
It was your dream-come-true moment.

641
00:35:10,860 --> 00:35:12,500
Why did you try to escape from the window?

642
00:35:12,500 --> 00:35:13,160
How stupid.

643
00:35:14,940 --> 00:35:16,470
Beijing is so big.

644
00:35:16,650 --> 00:35:18,460
As long as you keep your mouths shut,

645
00:35:18,460 --> 00:35:20,720
people will stop gossiping in a few days.

646
00:35:20,860 --> 00:35:22,320
Just keep it a secret.

647
00:35:23,460 --> 00:35:25,390
If this had happened in my village,

648
00:35:25,420 --> 00:35:27,280
that man wouldn't be able to live.

649
00:35:29,530 --> 00:35:31,560
I can't live like this, either.

650
00:35:34,570 --> 00:35:35,590
After wiping your ass,

651
00:35:35,590 --> 00:35:37,000
you're putting it back in?

652
00:35:37,000 --> 00:35:38,860
There are no unused cotton swabs.

653
00:35:40,010 --> 00:35:42,870
You can keep this medicine for yourself
from now on.

654
00:35:43,260 --> 00:35:44,720
Then buy a new bottle of it.

655
00:35:45,090 --> 00:35:45,950
Hello, Mr. Chu.

656
00:35:48,440 --> 00:35:49,650
Around 5 PM today,

657
00:35:49,730 --> 00:35:51,090
a woman might come looking for me.

658
00:35:51,090 --> 00:35:52,160
When she arrives,

659
00:35:52,550 --> 00:35:54,010
ask her to go straight to my room.

660
00:35:54,010 --> 00:35:55,210
I mean it's possible.

661
00:35:55,960 --> 00:35:56,760
I understand.

662
00:35:58,340 --> 00:35:59,670
What do you understand?

663
00:36:00,280 --> 00:36:01,110
A pretty girl.

664
00:36:02,360 --> 00:36:03,290
It's different.

665
00:36:03,440 --> 00:36:04,900
It's different this time.

666
00:36:05,130 --> 00:36:05,760
When she arrives,

667
00:36:05,760 --> 00:36:06,480
give me a call first

668
00:36:06,480 --> 00:36:07,280
to let me know.

669
00:36:07,860 --> 00:36:08,280
Okay.

670
00:36:09,980 --> 00:36:10,550
And also,

671
00:36:11,480 --> 00:36:12,010
Zheng.

672
00:36:13,300 --> 00:36:14,840
Watch your tongue from now on.

673
00:36:14,840 --> 00:36:16,040
Don't be so flippant.

674
00:36:36,190 --> 00:36:36,690
Hello.

675
00:36:37,300 --> 00:36:39,150
Mr. Chu, Miss Shen is here.

676
00:36:39,760 --> 00:36:41,150
She has already gone upstairs.

677
00:36:41,150 --> 00:36:41,630
Got it.

678
00:37:09,530 --> 00:37:10,740
Whether an actor

679
00:37:11,130 --> 00:37:12,310
can succeed or not

680
00:37:13,060 --> 00:37:15,720
mainly depends on
acting skills and resources.

681
00:37:15,880 --> 00:37:17,170
Even if you are extremely capable,

682
00:37:17,170 --> 00:37:19,230
without resources, it's all in vain.

683
00:37:22,590 --> 00:37:24,120
Do you want to be an actress?

684
00:37:24,340 --> 00:37:26,540
As long as you are confident and want it,

685
00:37:26,840 --> 00:37:28,110
I'll use my resources

686
00:37:28,110 --> 00:37:29,090
to bet with them.

687
00:37:29,920 --> 00:37:31,380
I'm sure it'll succeed.

688
00:37:34,380 --> 00:37:35,320
But the key is...

689
00:37:37,360 --> 00:37:38,820
whether you want it or not.

690
00:38:27,690 --> 00:38:28,550
I like you.

691
00:38:29,260 --> 00:38:29,980
I love you.

692
00:38:31,730 --> 00:38:32,730
I want to give you

693
00:38:32,730 --> 00:38:34,060
what I think is the best.

694
00:38:34,860 --> 00:38:35,990
You like acting.

695
00:38:37,630 --> 00:38:38,430
In the future,

696
00:38:38,760 --> 00:38:41,480
you will definitely become a famous

697
00:38:41,940 --> 00:38:43,140
and great actress.

698
00:38:44,050 --> 00:38:46,110
You will definitely hit the big time.

699
00:39:27,900 --> 00:39:28,900
She's a good girl.

700
00:39:33,240 --> 00:39:33,830
Mr. Chu.

701
00:39:33,860 --> 00:39:35,400
This is a fruit platter for you
from the hotel.

702
00:39:35,400 --> 00:39:35,960
No need.

703
00:39:39,050 --> 00:39:40,210
In matters of love,

704
00:39:40,230 --> 00:39:42,230
the most important thing is timing.

705
00:39:42,260 --> 00:39:44,190
It's a now-or-never opportunity.

706
00:39:44,530 --> 00:39:46,050
The most crucial thing right now

707
00:39:46,050 --> 00:39:47,910
is controlling public opinions.

708
00:39:47,940 --> 00:39:49,460
But don't worry about that.

709
00:39:49,460 --> 00:39:51,590
I'm the only big-mouthed man
in the Seasons Change Hostel.

710
00:39:51,590 --> 00:39:52,670
If I can control it,

711
00:39:53,050 --> 00:39:54,030
this matter of yours

712
00:39:54,030 --> 00:39:56,160
will basically be under control, too.

713
00:39:58,860 --> 00:39:59,840
Ranran is back.

714
00:40:00,050 --> 00:40:04,330
[Registration Room]

715
00:40:01,110 --> 00:40:02,230
I've been standing outside
for a long time.

716
00:40:02,230 --> 00:40:02,880
I'm freezing to death.

717
00:40:02,880 --> 00:40:05,080
I need to go inside the house to get warm.

718
00:40:08,340 --> 00:40:10,600
[Registration Room]

719
00:40:13,240 --> 00:40:15,520
[Registration Room]

720
00:40:36,110 --> 00:40:37,000
Ranran.

721
00:40:37,900 --> 00:40:40,430
I want to explain
what happened this morning.

722
00:40:41,650 --> 00:40:42,710
I, Tao Liangliang,

723
00:40:44,490 --> 00:40:46,820
am a man who dares to take responsibility.

724
00:41:08,030 --> 00:41:09,560
There's no need to explain.

725
00:41:12,940 --> 00:41:14,010
I'm going in first.

726
00:41:44,430 --> 00:41:51,830
[Registration Room]

727
00:42:09,730 --> 00:42:10,360
Xiaobao!

728
00:42:12,590 --> 00:42:13,320
Xiaobao!

729
00:42:13,880 --> 00:42:14,770
Hongmei.

730
00:42:15,130 --> 00:42:17,060
They're too heavy for you to carry.

731
00:42:17,440 --> 00:42:17,970
Alright.

732
00:42:18,440 --> 00:42:20,370
They're too heavy for you to carry.

733
00:42:20,630 --> 00:42:21,690
Alright, alright.

734
00:42:22,190 --> 00:42:22,730
Hongmei.

735
00:42:23,920 --> 00:42:24,820
Alright.

736
00:42:25,780 --> 00:42:26,900
This is the stuff

737
00:42:26,960 --> 00:42:28,620
Zongbao asked me to bring you.

738
00:42:28,920 --> 00:42:30,850
Look at all these bags and bundles.

739
00:42:30,900 --> 00:42:31,580
Hongmei!

740
00:42:31,800 --> 00:42:34,690
He really misses you two.

741
00:42:35,690 --> 00:42:36,530
Alright.

742
00:42:37,710 --> 00:42:41,880
Mom,
my dad asked him to bring them for us.

743
00:42:42,630 --> 00:42:44,960
My dad misses us.

744
00:42:45,400 --> 00:42:47,550
Hongmei, Zongbao said

745
00:42:47,690 --> 00:42:49,780
he wouldn't wire the money this time.

746
00:42:50,130 --> 00:42:51,960
He heard I was coming back,

747
00:42:52,440 --> 00:42:53,170
so he asked me

748
00:42:53,230 --> 00:42:54,910
to bring it for you directly.
